OL,3,CState pension errors 'could be
OL,4,Cvirtually impossible to fix if records
OL,5,Cdeleted'
OL,7,FConcerns that some state pension
OL,8,Frecords could be deleted, making it
OL,9,F"virtually impossible" to correct past
OL,10,Ferrors in payments, have been raised
OL,11,Fby a former minister.
OL,13,FMultiple errors in state pension
OL,14,Fpayments have been spotlighted in
OL,15,Frecent years and in some cases the
OL,16,Fpeople affected died before they could
OL,17,Fbe put right.
OL,19,FErrors can potentially be fixed even
OL,20,Fafter someone has died, with the money
OL,21,Fdue going to heirs.
