OL,3,CState pension errors 'could be
OL,4,Cvirtually impossible to fix if records
OL,5,Cdeleted'
OL,7,FSir Steve Webb, a former Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrat pensions minister, said he
OL,9,Fhas written to the permanent secretary
OL,10,Fat the Department for Work and
OL,11,FPensions (DWP), Sir Peter Schofield,
OL,12,Fasking him to ensure that records are
OL,13,Fretained for as long as they may be
OL,14,Fneeded to clear up any outstanding
OL,15,Fstate pension errors.
