OL,7,FThe FOI reply said: "Application of
OL,8,Fthe standard retention policy remains
OL,9,Fpaused.
OL,11,F"Once the embargo is lifted, then we
OL,12,Fwill look at deletion of records that
OL,13,Fare no longer required and re-apply
OL,14,Fthe retention policy."
