OL,7,FSir Steve, who is now a partner at
OL,8,Fconsultants LCP (Lane Clark & Peacock)
OL,9,Fsaid that, with around 500,000 people
OL,10,Fover state pension age dying each
OL,11,Fyear, a decision to now delete data
OL,12,Ffor deaths in 2017 to 2020 inclusive,
OL,13,Fwhich were originally retained but are
OL,14,Fmore than four years old, could
OL,15,Fpotentially lead to as many as two
OL,16,Fmillion records being wiped.
