OL,3,CState pension errors 'could be
OL,4,Cvirtually impossible to fix if records
OL,5,Cdeleted'
OL,7,FHe said some of these would include
OL,8,Fwomen who had missed out on "home
OL,9,Fresponsibilities protection" ` a
OL,10,Fscheme to help protect parents' and
OL,11,Fcarers' state pension ` whose families
OL,12,Fmay be unable to have the situation
OL,13,Fcorrected.
OL,15,FSir Steve pointed to previously-
OL,16,Freleased DWP figures indicating that
OL,17,Fout of an estimated 194,000 people
OL,18,Faffected by errors relating to home
OL,19,Fresponsibilities protection, 43,000
OL,20,Fdied having never benefited from the
OL,21,Fprotection.
