OL,7,FThose who were deceased were underpaid
OL,8,Fan estimated #127 million.
OL,10,FSir Steve urged people who believe
OL,11,Fthere may have been errors to have
OL,12,Ftheir records checked.
OL,14,FHe said: "I often hear from people who
OL,15,Fare trying to sort out errors in the
OL,16,Fstate pension of loved ones who are no
OL,17,Flonger with us, but are told nothing
OL,18,Fcan be done because the records have
OL,19,Fbeen destroyed.
