OL,5,Cdeleted'
OL,7,F"Whilst we cannot get back the records
OL,8,Fthat have already been deleted, it is
OL,9,Fessential that DWP does not now delete
OL,10,Fmillions more records, especially
OL,11,Fgiven the live process of trying to
OL,12,Ffix errors around home
OL,13,Fresponsibilities protection.
OL,15,F"The least we can do for people who
OL,16,Fwere never paid the right pension is
OL,17,Fto do all we can to make sure that at
OL,18,Fleast their families get the money
OL,19,Fthey missed out on."
